{
  "stem": "1641.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was sent to a place near-- near Budapest, only about 100 kilometers away, where we had to get up very early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to walk about 15 kilometers to our workplace, with our rucksack-- backpack in-- in English.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there we had to work mostly cutting out trees, putting trees on tracks and-- oh, physical labor, all different types of physical labor.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's what it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we walked back in the evenings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was hard work, but the-- but the food was not too bad.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was only a very short period that this lasted.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And after about four weeks doing this, we-- the order came that we have-- our group has been-- has been ordered to go by train to the border, to the Hungarian-Russian border, to Transylvania, up to the high Carpathian Mountains.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we all had together-- together, we had a bit of bread left, maybe a bit of saus-- you know, Hungarian-- like [HUNGARIAN] type sausages.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was enough for about two days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we took the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went 12 hours to the east.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there we had to change trains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had-- our train didn't go any further.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to pick up another train, which would have taken us up to the high Carpathian Mountains, to a position-- we knew where we were going.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a position about 50 miles from the front line, where the Russians were pressing their attacks against the Hungarian army.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we got off the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were inquiring which-- which track is the other train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And at that stage, we were standing out there, about 200 of us, all 20, 21 year old, when two tall men in leather jackets came to our Hungarian commander.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
